data.description: Need Help with your Closing Costs, Check out this home.... Ranch home in the convenient location of Raintree Place Subdivision. Just a short drive to all the local shops and amenities of Gulf Shores and Foley, and the beautiful Gulf Shore Beaches. Large Master Bedroom with EnSuite, an oversized walk-in closet, located separately from the other 2 very spacious bedrooms. Open concept great for entertaining. Enjoy the living room with vaulted ceilings, wood burning fireplace, which can be converted to gas (already plumbed), perfect for the upcoming game days. If entertaining outdoors is your desire, perfect screened in porch just off the kitchen/living.  Also, a he/she shed for all of your toys and tools. Perfect fenced backyard great for grilling, that opens up to the community common area, so your backyard feels massive. Perfect place to walk your pets, get some exercise or fish with the kids. Large laundry room with the washer and dryer conveying with the purchase of the move in ready home. Call me to schedule your private tour today.
